{{vgname|荣誉勋章：空降神兵|en=Medal of Honor: Airborne|official-cn=荣誉勋章：神兵天降|2=民间普遍采用台译名}}是一款由[[EALA|EALA]]开发的[[二战|二战]]题材[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]，为[[荣誉勋章系列|荣誉勋章系列]]的第11部正传。游戏分别于2007年9月与11月在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]与 [[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]平台发行<ref name="ps3date">{{cite web | url = http://ps3.ign.com/objects/692/692471.html | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2007-08-07 | title = Medal of Honor: Airborne Game Profile | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | archive-date = 2012-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118070259/http://ps3.ign.com/objects/692/692471.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。原本计划的[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]和[[Wii|Wii]]版本于2007年取消<ref name="pcreleasedate">{{cite web| url = http://planetmedalofhonor.gamespy.com/fullstory.php?id=124716| publisher = Planet Medal of Honor| date = 2007-08-02| title = MOH: Airborne Release Date Pushed Back| accessdate = 2007-11-01| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071027174106/http://planetmedalofhonor.gamespy.com/fullstory.php?id=124716| archivedate = 2007-10-27}}</ref>，《[[荣誉勋章：先锋|荣誉勋章：先锋]]》则代替其发行于上述游戏机上。游戏故事发生在[[第二次世界大战欧洲战场|第二次世界大战欧洲战场]]，并且为该系列第一款着重刻画[[伞兵|伞兵]]的游戏<ref>Casey Lynch, "''Medal of Honor: Airborne'': Don't give up on WWII shooters just yet," ''PlayStation: The Official Magazine'' 003 (February 2008): 80-81.</ref>。

遊戲中，玩家將扮演一名服役於美軍第82空降師，名叫Boyd Travers的傘兵，並參與盟軍對西西里，諾曼第和德國本土的反攻。值得一提的是，較少為其他二戰類射擊遊戲所著墨的市場花園行動也被收錄在本作當中。

